    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Building block to be used with other similar building blocks in the construction of buildings. May be made of a variety of materials in a variety of shapes and sizes. Often standardized and/or modular.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
